Teorema de Bayes

\[P(A\cap B^c)=P(A\mid B^c) P(B^c)\]

\[P(B\mid A) = \frac{P(B\cap A)}{P(A)} = \frac{P(A\mid B)P(B)}{P(A\mid B)P(B) + P(A\mid B^c)P(B^c)}\]
